title: Openstreetmap, Berlin Railways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Berlin Railways, Germany, 2008
description: This data was provided by openstreetmaps and shows the locations of the Railway infrastructure in the Berlin administrative area in the country of Germany. Railways include trams, subways, and standard trains. This railways data set was uploaded as a poly line shape file and includes attribute information for Feature name and feature type.
